**(1)** uses the **present continuous tense**, which is the **wrong tense** because of the keyword "since".
**(2)** has a mismatched **plural verb** and the **wrong tense**.
**(4)** uses a mismatched **plural verb** ("have"), but "news" requires a **singular verb**.

